"If you have set up your browser to not save cookies, you need to enable "
"saving them (at least for this site, or 'same-origin' requests)."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du har indstillet din browser til ikke at gemme cookies, skal du "
"aktivere det (i hvert fald for dette websted eller 'same-origin'-"
